files.description: The sole EHI export documentation: a 10-page PDF containing the b(10) export data dictionary. Documents 15 CSV export sections (demographics, allergies, vitals, care team, immunizations, procedures, assessment/plan, labs, provenance, medications, smoking status, clinical notes, goals, health concerns, problems) with column names, data types, and minimal notes. Created June 2022, approved by Anthony Puglisi.
